==English==

====Noun====
'''criterion''' (''plural'' '''[[criteria]]''')

# A [[standard]] or [[test]] by which [[individual]] [[thing]]s or [[people]] may be [[compare]]d and [[judge]]d.

====Usage notes====
Although common, the singular use of [[criteria]] is considered incorrect.

